{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"act28side_level_act28side_07_beg","storyGroup":"act28side","storySort":15,"storyDependence":"act28side_level_act28side_06_end","storyCanShow":1,"storyCode":"CV-7","storyName":"白热","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"看着一拨拨离开地块的居民去往拓荒地，杰西卡最终下定了决心，帮助当地居民从银行手中夺回属于自己的钱财。","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"activities/act28side/level_act28side_07_beg","avgTag":"行动前","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"act28side_07","minState":"PLAYED","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":13,"next":15,"characters":["罗拉","迈尔斯","杰西卡","车队首领","里昂","海伦娜","伍德洛","西尔维娅"]},"lines":[{"type":"header","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","id":0},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":1},{"type":"stopmusic","id":2},{"type":"dialog","id":3},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":4},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e1/Avg_bg_bg_snow_2.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":5},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$distressed_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_distressed_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":6,"musicid":0},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_snowstormlp","loop":"true","channel":"b","volume":"0","id":7},{"type":"soundvolume","volume":"0.4","fadetime":"3","channel":"b","id":8},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":9},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":10},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_1043_1#1$1","duration":"1","id":11},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1042_1#1$1","duration":"1","id":12},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":13},{"type":"charslot","duration":"1","id":14},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":15},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1042_1#1$1","duration":"1","id":16},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":17},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1042_1#1$1","duration":"1","id":18},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":19},{"type":"charslot","duration":"0.5","id":20},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":21},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_4105_almond_1#2$1","duration":"1","id":22},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_1034_jesca2_1#1$1","duration":"1","id":23},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":24},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","posfrom":"0,0","posto":"-50,0","duration":"1","afrom":"1","ato":"0","id":25},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","posfrom":"0,0","posto":"50,0","duration":"1","afrom":"1","ato":"0","id":26},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":27},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1038_1#1$1","duration":"1.5","id":28},{"type":"delay","time":"2.5","id":29},{"type":"charslot","id":30},{"type":"text","text":"新年已过，但达维镇的风雪依然冰冷刺骨，不带一丝暖意。","id":31},{"type":"text","text":"站在地块外等车的人群中间，迈尔斯迷迷糊糊地想，在寒风里等车，似乎是很久以前的事了。","id":32},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4105_almond_1#2$1","id":33},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗拉","text":"老爷子，你们要去的拓荒地，到底是个什么样的地方？","id":34,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/34/Avg_avg_4105_almond_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1038_1#8$1","id":35},{"type":"dialogue","name":"迈尔斯","text":"......至少应该比达维镇暖和。","id":36,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/84/Avg_avg_npc_1038_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"迈尔斯","text":"别替我担心了，他们至少还算留了点情面，让我能和老邻居们埋在一起。","id":37,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/84/Avg_avg_npc_1038_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1034_jesca2_1#9$1","id":38},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰西卡","text":"抱歉......抱歉......","id":39,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/26/Avg_avg_1034_jesca2_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1038_1#8$1","id":40},{"type":"dialogue","name":"迈尔斯","text":"孩子，既然一切都已经改变不了了，不如想想别的事情，别钻这个牛角尖。","id":41,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/84/Avg_avg_npc_1038_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1038_1#2$1","id":42},{"type":"dialogue","name":"迈尔斯","text":"比如，我刚刚想起来，上次这么等车，还是去别的移动城市给我小妹妹奔丧那次。","id":43,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9f/Avg_avg_npc_1038_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"迈尔斯","text":"也是这么冷的天，海伦娜、伍德洛、里昂，三个人陪我一起等车队来。","id":44,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9f/Avg_avg_npc_1038_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1038_1#8$1","id":45},{"type":"dialogue","name":"迈尔斯","text":"我拿着海伦娜餐厅花瓶里攒起来的花束，披着里昂借我的旧礼服，冻了好几个小时。","id":46,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/84/Avg_avg_npc_1038_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"迈尔斯","text":"说来也怪，我连等车那天伍德洛胡子多长都记得清清楚楚，可上了车之后，一切都模模糊糊的，好像隔着一层毛玻璃似的。","id":47,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/84/Avg_avg_npc_1038_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1038_1#10$1","id":48},{"type":"dialogue","name":"迈尔斯","text":"我好像去了很大的移动城市，又觉得那里还没达维镇大；我好像哭了一场，又好像没哭出来......","id":49,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/72/Avg_avg_npc_1038_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1038_1#6$1","id":50},{"type":"dialogue","name":"迈尔斯","text":"再之后，就只剩我从回达维镇的车上下来，他们把我扶下车的事了。","id":51,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/45/Avg_avg_npc_1038_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1038_1#8$1","id":52},{"type":"dialogue","name":"迈尔斯","text":"之后的事我反而又都能记起来了，我去海伦娜那儿喝了不少酒，醉得很厉害，连那天晚上的醉话我还记得一清二楚......","id":53,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/84/Avg_avg_npc_1038_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","duration":"1","id":54},{"type":"dialog","id":55},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_truckengine","loop":"true","channel":"a","volume":"0","id":56},{"type":"soundvolume","volume":"0.6","fadetime":"3","channel":"a","id":57},{"type":"delay","time":"3","id":58},{"type":"dialogue","name":"车队首领","text":"往拓荒地去的车队到了！达维镇的人，开始上车了！","id":59},{"type":"soundvolume","volume":"0","fadetime":"1","channel":"b","id":60},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"a","fadetime":"3","id":61},{"type":"dialog","id":62},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":63},{"type":"charslot","id":64},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":65},{"type":"text","text":"“我最疼的小妹妹也没了，从此之后，我就和达维镇绑死在一起了，妈的。”","id":66},{"type":"text","text":"“里昂，听见了吗，我要在地块上老死！到那时候......”","id":67},{"type":"dialog","id":68},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1035_1#2$1","focus":"n","id":69},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4a/Avg_bg_42_g3_diner.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":70},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":71},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":72},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"20","ystrength":"20","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":73},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1035_1#4$1","id":74},{"type":"dialogue","name":"里昂","text":"迈尔斯，别以为我记不住！","id":75,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e1/Avg_avg_npc_1035_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1035_1#6$1","id":76},{"type":"dialogue","name":"里昂","text":"你说：“到那时候，麻烦你把我推进动力炉里，我倒要看看自己的骨灰......能不能呛得达维镇......打个喷嚏......”","id":77,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ab/Avg_avg_npc_1035_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_plateplace","id":78},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"n","id":79},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.2","xstrength":"20","ystrength":"10","vibrato":"20","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":80},{"type":"text","text":"工程师仰起头，又往嘴里灌了一大口。","id":81},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1035_1#6$1","id":82},{"type":"dialogue","name":"里昂","text":"你刚说完，达维镇还没怎么样，我先打了个惊天动地的喷嚏。","id":83,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ab/Avg_avg_npc_1035_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1035_1#3$1","id":84},{"type":"dialogue","name":"里昂","text":"哈哈，哈哈哈......","id":85,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/26/Avg_avg_npc_1035_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1035_1#6$1","id":86},{"type":"dialogue","name":"里昂","text":"当年谁也没笑，谁都笑不出来，可我现在觉得这事真他妈滑稽，你不觉得吗？","id":87,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ab/Avg_avg_npc_1035_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1035_1#7$1","id":88},{"type":"dialogue","name":"里昂","text":"别不说话呀！喝，迈尔斯，喝！","id":89,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b6/Avg_avg_npc_1035_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":90},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":91},{"type":"charslot","id":92},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e1/Avg_bg_bg_snow_2.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":93},{"type":"soundvolume","volume":"0.4","fadetime":"2","channel":"b","id":94},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":95},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_snowrun","id":96},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1034_1#1$1","duration":"1","id":97},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4104_coldst_1#2$1","duration":"1","id":98},{"type":"delay","time":"1.6","id":99},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4104_coldst_1#2$1","focus":"l","id":100},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海伦娜","text":"抱歉......我们来迟了。","id":101,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9e/Avg_avg_4104_coldst_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":102},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1034_jesca2_1#1$1","id":103},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰西卡","text":"伍德洛先生，海伦娜女士......里昂先生呢？","id":104,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/44/Avg_avg_1034_jesca2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":105},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4104_coldst_1#2$1","focus":"l","id":106},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1034_1#10$1","focus":"l","id":107},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海伦娜","text":"我们临出门之前，他说自己只需要一些时间，想通了会过来的......说完就又给自己开了一瓶。","id":108,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9e/Avg_avg_4104_coldst_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1034_1#10$1","focus":"r","id":109},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伍德洛","text":"......可我们哪还有时间。","id":110,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/eb/Avg_avg_npc_1034_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":111},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1038_1#3$1","id":112},{"type":"dialogue","name":"迈尔斯","text":"没什么，这对他......或许也算好事。","id":113,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/78/Avg_avg_npc_1038_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":114},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"n","id":115},{"type":"soundvolume","volume":"1","fadetime":"1","channel":"b","id":116},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":117},{"type":"soundvolume","volume":"0.5","fadetime":"1","channel":"b","id":118},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1038_1#10$1","id":119},{"type":"dialogue","name":"迈尔斯","text":"嘶，这鬼天气......怎么就这么冷！","id":120,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/72/Avg_avg_npc_1038_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1034_1#1$1","id":121},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伍德洛","text":"等上了车，你就可以和这里的鬼天气说再见了。","id":122,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/61/Avg_avg_npc_1034_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1034_jesca2_1#3$1","id":123},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰西卡","text":"伍德洛先生！","id":124,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/72/Avg_avg_1034_jesca2_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1038_1#1$1","id":125},{"type":"dialogue","name":"迈尔斯","text":"他没说错。","id":126,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b4/Avg_avg_npc_1038_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1034_jesca2_1#9$1","id":127},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰西卡","text":"抱歉......","id":128,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/26/Avg_avg_1034_jesca2_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1038_1#7$1","id":129},{"type":"dialogue","name":"迈尔斯","text":"唉，杰西卡，你真的不用再道歉了。这件事里，银行有错，黑钢有错，就连我们也有不对的地方，唯独你......你没做错任何事情。","id":130,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ee/Avg_avg_npc_1038_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"迈尔斯","text":"所以，别自责了，毕竟我们从一开始，就不指望你能做到什么事情——","id":131,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ee/Avg_avg_npc_1038_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"n","id":132},{"type":"text","text":"迈尔斯立刻意识到自己的失言，他刚想解释什么，可车队首领已经拉住了他的手臂。","id":133},{"type":"charslot","id":134},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_truckengine","loop":"true","channel":"a","volume":"0.6","id":135},{"type":"dialogue","name":"车队首领","text":"老头儿，有什么话也不该留到现在再说，就差你一个了，赶紧上车！","id":136},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1038_1#6$1","id":137},{"type":"dialogue","name":"迈尔斯","text":"杰西卡，我......","id":138,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/45/Avg_avg_npc_1038_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":139},{"type":"dialogue","name":"车队首领","text":"再拖下去，在荒地上遇见锈锤或者天灾什么的，到时候你负责吗？","id":140},{"type":"dialogue","name":"车队首领","text":"走了！","id":141},{"type":"dialog","id":142},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_snowbootwalk","id":143},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1038_1#1$1","id":144},{"type":"charslot","duration":"1","id":145},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":146},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"a","fadetime":"3","id":147},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":148},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4104_coldst_1#5$1","id":149},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海伦娜","text":"杰西卡，你别误会，迈尔斯他不是这个意思。","id":150,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/35/Avg_avg_4104_coldst_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1034_jesca2_1#9$1","id":151},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰西卡","text":"我知道......可他说得没错......","id":152,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/26/Avg_avg_1034_jesca2_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1034_jesca2_1#7$1","id":153},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰西卡","text":"我或许是做了很多事，但最后......什么都没做成。","id":154,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7f/Avg_avg_1034_jesca2_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1034_jesca2_1#2$1","id":155},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰西卡","text":"......什么都没改变。","id":156,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a1/Avg_avg_1034_jesca2_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":157},{"type":"dialog","id":158},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"b","fadetime":"2","id":159},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":160},{"type":"charslot","id":161},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":162},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1035_1#1$1","focus":"n","id":163},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4a/Avg_bg_42_g3_diner.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":164},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":165},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_doorbell","id":166},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":167},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1035_1#10$1","id":168},{"type":"dialogue","name":"里昂","text":"谁呀？伍德洛吗？海伦娜吗？别催了，我都说我想通了，我这不是要去送迈尔斯了——","id":169,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/04/Avg_avg_npc_1035_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":170},{"type":"charslot","id":171},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$sjoyasorrow_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_sjoyasorrow_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":172,"musicid":1},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1039_1#4$1","duration":"1","id":173},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":174},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1035_1#10$1","id":175},{"type":"dialogue","name":"里昂","text":"怎么是你？！","id":176,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/04/Avg_avg_npc_1035_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1035_1#9$1","id":177},{"type":"dialogue","name":"里昂","text":"呵，怎么，你是来赶我的吗？","id":178,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/79/Avg_avg_npc_1035_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":179},{"type":"text","text":"西尔维娅并未像里昂见惯了的那样，道歉，低头，跑走。","id":180},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"0.6","id":181},{"type":"text","text":"她在原地站了一会儿，手紧紧攥着胸前的什么东西，然后僵硬地迈开腿，往餐厅里走去。","id":182},{"type":"text","text":"她一直走到餐台旁边的座位处，背对着餐馆门口坐下，眼睛直勾勾地看着前方的空座。","id":183},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1039_1#4$1","id":184},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西尔维娅","text":"里昂先生，伍德洛先生和海伦娜女士......他们还回来吗？","id":185,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4b/Avg_avg_npc_1039_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1035_1#10$1","id":186},{"type":"dialogue","name":"里昂","text":"伍德洛......海伦娜？跟你有什么关系？他们送迈尔斯去了——","id":187,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/04/Avg_avg_npc_1035_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"n","id":188},{"type":"text","text":"冷风从西尔维娅刚刚打开的门缝里钻进餐厅，呜咽着掠过空酒瓶的瓶口。","id":189},{"type":"text","text":"里昂打了个冷战。","id":190},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1035_1#8$1","id":191},{"type":"dialogue","name":"里昂","text":"他们送迈尔斯去了，一会儿会回来，但没人想找你，能听懂吗？能听懂就赶紧出去，让我......一个人静静。","id":192,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1f/Avg_avg_npc_1035_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1039_1#4$1","focus":"n","id":193},{"type":"text","text":"西尔维娅的十指在桌上紧紧扣在一起。","id":194},{"type":"text","text":"她咽了口口水，强迫自己转过头，注视里昂的脸，而里昂看见了她经常紧紧攥着的是什么东西。","id":195},{"type":"text","text":"一枚戒指，银色的，上面有几颗零零星星的碎钻。","id":196},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1039_1#4$1","id":197},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西尔维娅","text":"里昂先生，我不能——","id":198,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4b/Avg_avg_npc_1039_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1035_1#5$1","id":199},{"type":"dialogue","name":"里昂","text":"你脖子上挂着的戒指是谁给你的？","id":200,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1c/Avg_avg_npc_1035_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1039_1#1$1","id":201},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西尔维娅","text":"戒指？","id":202,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/31/Avg_avg_npc_1039_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1035_1#7$1","id":203},{"type":"dialogue","name":"里昂","text":"不可能是我，不可能是本尼......只可能是......","id":204,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b6/Avg_avg_npc_1035_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1035_1#6$1","id":205},{"type":"dialogue","name":"里昂","text":"......他？","id":206,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ab/Avg_avg_npc_1035_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":207},{"type":"text","text":"两人目光相接。","id":208},{"type":"text","text":"西尔维娅微微点了点头，重新攥紧了戒指，眼中显出某种近乎疯狂的坚定。","id":209},{"type":"text","text":"看着西尔维娅的眼睛，里昂回忆起卡尔的眼神。","id":210},{"type":"text","text":"他在出发前头天晚上消失了几个小时，回来的时候，眼神和自己面前这个人一模一样。","id":211},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":212},{"type":"dialog","id":213},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":214},{"type":"charslot","id":215},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":216},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a3/Avg_bg_42_g10_blacksteelarmory.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":217},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":218},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":219},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$drift_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_drift_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":220,"musicid":2},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4105_almond_1#2$1","duration":"1","id":221},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_1034_jesca2_1#1$1","duration":"1","id":222},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":223},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4105_almond_1#2$1","focus":"l","id":224},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗拉","text":"杰西卡，你也知道......我们小队一旦接到命令就要撤出达维镇。不管地块上发生了什么，我们都得回本舰去。","id":225,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/34/Avg_avg_4105_almond_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_1034_jesca2_1#9$1","focus":"r","id":226},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰西卡","text":"我知道，我知道......","id":227,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/26/Avg_avg_1034_jesca2_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_1034_jesca2_1#7$1","focus":"r","id":228},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰西卡","text":"我们要走了，迈尔斯先生已经走了，伍德洛先生和海伦娜女士也说会走，里昂先生也不太可能继续留下......大家都要走了。","id":229,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7f/Avg_avg_1034_jesca2_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰西卡","text":"可我......我为大家做了什么？","id":230,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7f/Avg_avg_1034_jesca2_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4105_almond_1#9$1","focus":"l","id":231},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗拉","text":"......就算连你自己都不认同，我还是要说，你在达维镇外围清理了混混，帮里昂保住了他的房子，让克里夫先生知道了银行越权的事......","id":232,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/be/Avg_avg_4105_almond_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_1034_jesca2_1#7$1","focus":"r","id":233},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰西卡","text":"......可到最后，一切都是徒劳，我......我辜负了所有人的期望......","id":234,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7f/Avg_avg_1034_jesca2_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰西卡","text":"或者更糟，就像迈尔斯先生说的那样......从一开始，就没人在我身上期望什么，全是我自己自作多情......","id":235,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7f/Avg_avg_1034_jesca2_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4105_almond_1#5$1","focus":"l","id":236},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗拉","text":"杰西卡！","id":237,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/be/Avg_avg_4105_almond_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_1034_jesca2_1#10$1","focus":"r","id":238},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰西卡","text":"不，就算是自作多情，我也......","id":239,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e3/Avg_avg_1034_jesca2_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_1034_jesca2_1#14$1","focus":"r","id":240},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰西卡","text":"......","id":241,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_1034_jesca2_1-14$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_1034_jesca2_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":242},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰西卡","text":"罗拉，我想出去转转。","id":243,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/44/Avg_avg_1034_jesca2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4105_almond_1#2$1","focus":"l","id":244},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗拉","text":"现在不是时候，我们马上就要回本舰了......我去帮你打包行李，你好好睡一觉，好了我来叫你，行吗？","id":245,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/34/Avg_avg_4105_almond_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_1034_jesca2_1#14$1","focus":"r","id":246},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰西卡","text":"......我得出去转转。","id":247,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_1034_jesca2_1-14$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4105_almond_1#2$1","focus":"l","id":248},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗拉","text":"去哪里？","id":249,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/34/Avg_avg_4105_almond_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_1034_jesca2_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":250},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰西卡","text":"我不知道。","id":251,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/44/Avg_avg_1034_jesca2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4105_almond_1#2$1","focus":"l","id":252},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗拉","text":"你确定？","id":253,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/34/Avg_avg_4105_almond_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_1034_jesca2_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":254},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰西卡","text":"嗯。","id":255,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/44/Avg_avg_1034_jesca2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4105_almond_1#3$1","focus":"l","id":256},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗拉","text":"......","id":257,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_avg_4105_almond_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4105_almond_1#9$1","focus":"l","id":258},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗拉","text":"早点回来，好吗？","id":259,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/be/Avg_avg_4105_almond_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_1034_jesca2_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":260},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰西卡","text":"我......尽量。","id":261,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/44/Avg_avg_1034_jesca2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":262},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":263},{"type":"charslot","id":264},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":265},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4a/Avg_bg_42_g3_diner.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":266},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":267},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":268},{"type":"playsound","key":"$dooropenquite","volume":"1","id":269},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1034_1#1$1","duration":"1","id":270},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4104_coldst_1#5$1","duration":"1","id":271},{"type":"delay","time":"1.6","id":272},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4104_coldst_1#5$1","focus":"l","id":273},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海伦娜","text":"里昂，别喝了——","id":274,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/35/Avg_avg_4104_coldst_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4104_coldst_1#8$1","focus":"l","id":275},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海伦娜","text":"——等等，你酒醒了？","id":276,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/27/Avg_avg_4104_coldst_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":277},{"type":"charslot","id":278},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1035_1#1$1","id":279},{"type":"dialogue","name":"里昂","text":"算是吧。","id":280,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0b/Avg_avg_npc_1035_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4104_coldst_1#2$1","id":281},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海伦娜","text":"那......西尔维娅呢，她有什么事？","id":282,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9e/Avg_avg_4104_coldst_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1035_1#1$1","id":283},{"type":"dialogue","name":"里昂","text":"她要等你们回来，跟我们三个一起说。","id":284,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0b/Avg_avg_npc_1035_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":285},{"type":"charslot","id":286},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":287},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_clothmovement","volume":"0.6","id":288},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1039_1#4$1","duration":"0.7","posfrom":"0,-30","posto":"0,0","id":289},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":290},{"type":"text","text":"西尔维娅从座位上站起身，戒指被她攥得很紧。白皙的手上，青色的血管清晰可见。","id":291},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1039_1#1$1","id":292},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西尔维娅","text":"海伦娜女士，伍德洛先生，里昂先生......","id":293,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/31/Avg_avg_npc_1039_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西尔维娅","text":"我......","id":294,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/31/Avg_avg_npc_1039_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1039_1#4$1","id":295},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西尔维娅","text":"我知道......银行里面有一笔钱。","id":296,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4b/Avg_avg_npc_1039_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1034_1#1$1","id":297},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伍德洛","text":"银行里面永远都有钱，西尔维娅，这不用你说。","id":298,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/61/Avg_avg_npc_1034_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1039_1#4$1","id":299},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西尔维娅","text":"我是说......黑钢给银行送来了一大笔库存资金，正锁在银行的......保险库里。","id":300,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4b/Avg_avg_npc_1039_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1035_1#10$1","id":301},{"type":"dialogue","name":"里昂","text":"为什么？","id":302,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/04/Avg_avg_npc_1035_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1039_1#4$1","id":303},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西尔维娅","text":"银行要为达维镇的新居民做准备。","id":304,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4b/Avg_avg_npc_1039_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1039_1#8$1","id":305},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西尔维娅","text":"他们清空整个地块，就是为了迎接那些和新产业配套的精密技工、研发人员、管理人员......","id":306,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/8a/Avg_avg_npc_1039_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西尔维娅","text":"为了满足他们的存贷款需求，现在银行里的钱......比平常多得多。","id":307,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/8a/Avg_avg_npc_1039_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西尔维娅","text":"多到......甚至可以让许多人在拓荒地......重新开始。","id":308,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/8a/Avg_avg_npc_1039_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西尔维娅","text":"......就是这样。","id":309,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/8a/Avg_avg_npc_1039_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1035_1#1$1","id":310},{"type":"dialogue","name":"里昂","text":"就是这样？西尔维娅，你到底什么意思？","id":311,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0b/Avg_avg_npc_1035_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4104_coldst_1#3$1","id":312},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海伦娜","text":"......里昂，如果你的酒醒了，你就不会问这种话。","id":313,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c4/Avg_avg_4104_coldst_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1035_1#8$1","id":314},{"type":"dialogue","name":"里昂","text":"......","id":315,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1f/Avg_avg_npc_1035_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1034_1#5$1","id":316},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伍德洛","text":"可我们不能不问。","id":317,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_1034_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伍德洛","text":"如果西尔维娅想的事情真的和我猜的一样，就更不能不问了。","id":318,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_1034_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伍德洛","text":"西尔维娅小姐，请问，你是否想要我们把那笔钱还给它们真正的主人？","id":319,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_1034_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伍德洛","text":"你是否想要我们把那笔钱......","id":320,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_1034_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":321},{"type":"dialog","id":322},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1034_1#5$1","id":323},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":324},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1034_1#6$1","id":325},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伍德洛","text":"抢出来？","id":326,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/31/Avg_avg_npc_1034_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":327},{"type":"charslot","id":328},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":329},{"type":"text","text":"西尔维娅以几乎难以辨认的幅度微微点了点头，然后用手摩挲着胸前的戒指，开始等待审判的降临。","id":330},{"type":"text","text":"餐厅里一片死寂。","id":331},{"type":"dialog","id":332},{"type":"playmusic","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/avg/m_avg_formal_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":333,"musicid":3},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4104_coldst_1#6$1","id":334},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":335},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海伦娜","text":"......至少现在大家在想同一件事了。","id":336,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/26/Avg_avg_4104_coldst_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海伦娜","text":"里昂，你赞成，还是反对？","id":337,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/26/Avg_avg_4104_coldst_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1035_1#8$1","id":338},{"type":"dialogue","name":"里昂","text":"......","id":339,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1f/Avg_avg_npc_1035_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4104_coldst_1#6$1","id":340},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海伦娜","text":"说句话。","id":341,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/26/Avg_avg_4104_coldst_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1035_1#7$1","id":342},{"type":"dialogue","name":"里昂","text":"不，我......我知道这笔钱是我们的，可......我也不想变成和那帮混混一样为非作歹的混蛋。","id":343,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b6/Avg_avg_npc_1035_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1034_1#6$1","id":344},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伍德洛","text":"达维镇为非作歹最多的混蛋从来都不是那些混混。","id":345,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/31/Avg_avg_npc_1034_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4104_coldst_1#6$1","id":346},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海伦娜","text":"所以你是赞成西尔维娅的了，伍德洛？","id":347,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/26/Avg_avg_4104_coldst_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1034_1#2$1","id":348},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伍德洛","text":"......不。","id":349,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e3/Avg_avg_npc_1034_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4104_coldst_1#8$1","id":350},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海伦娜","text":"“不”？！","id":351,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/27/Avg_avg_4104_coldst_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1034_1#1$1","id":352},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伍德洛","text":"我赞赏西尔维娅的勇气，同时觉得我们没有胜算。","id":353,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/61/Avg_avg_npc_1034_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伍德洛","text":"比如说，西尔维娅，你有银行的地图吗？","id":354,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/61/Avg_avg_npc_1034_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1039_1#1$1","id":355},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西尔维娅","text":"......有。","id":356,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/31/Avg_avg_npc_1039_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1034_1#1$1","id":357},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伍德洛","text":"拿出来。","id":358,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/61/Avg_avg_npc_1034_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1039_1#1$1","id":359},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西尔维娅","text":"我拿不出纸质地图，但我知道，从银行大门口到全楼总开关，要走一百步，按我的步幅是六十一米......","id":360,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/31/Avg_avg_npc_1039_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1039_1#3$1","id":361},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西尔维娅","text":"中间要拐三次弯，分别在四十四步、七十四步、九十三步处，标志物是盆栽、落地灯、柜台。","id":362,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4e/Avg_avg_npc_1039_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西尔维娅","text":"从总开关到保险库入口要经过会客室，过一扇暗门，下一个三十六级的楼梯，下楼梯后是一条直路，中间的步数分别是......","id":363,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4e/Avg_avg_npc_1039_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4104_coldst_1#11$1","id":364},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海伦娜","text":"西尔维娅......你......难道你把这些东西硬背下来了？！","id":365,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/54/Avg_avg_4104_coldst_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1034_1#1$1","id":366},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伍德洛","text":"不像。","id":367,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/61/Avg_avg_npc_1034_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伍德洛","text":"西尔维娅，从你的座位到餐厅门口有多远？","id":368,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/61/Avg_avg_npc_1034_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1039_1#1$1","id":369},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西尔维娅","text":"我刚刚走了十八步，在第六步之后向右拐了一个直角弯。总长约十一米。","id":370,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/31/Avg_avg_npc_1039_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1034_1#1$1","id":371},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伍德洛","text":"她不是硬背......她只是像这样，走了无数遍。","id":372,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/61/Avg_avg_npc_1034_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4104_coldst_1#6$1","id":373},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海伦娜","text":"伍德洛，你现在觉得我们有几成胜算？算上你呢？算上里昂呢？","id":374,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/26/Avg_avg_4104_coldst_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1034_1#1$1","id":375},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伍德洛","text":"......","id":376,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/61/Avg_avg_npc_1034_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伍德洛","text":"可我们怎么把钱送到拓荒地，又怎么抹去这笔钱的踪迹？","id":377,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/61/Avg_avg_npc_1034_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4104_coldst_1#6$1","id":378},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海伦娜","text":"这件事我来做。","id":379,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/26/Avg_avg_4104_coldst_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1034_1#10$1","id":380},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伍德洛","text":"我相信你能在荒地上活下来，可那笔钱......？","id":381,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/eb/Avg_avg_npc_1034_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":382},{"type":"text","text":"海伦娜叹了口气。她轻巧地翻进吧台，拿起桌上的餐刀，弯下腰撬动地板。","id":383},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_chairrub","volume":"1","id":384},{"type":"text","text":"吱嘎，吱嘎......","id":385},{"type":"text","text":"嘣。","id":386},{"type":"text","text":"她脚下腾起一团历史悠久的灰尘。","id":387},{"type":"dialog","id":388},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4104_coldst_1#2$2","duration":"0.5","id":389},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":390},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海伦娜","text":"不要以为能在跑水的时候找到那个箱子就算彻底了解我了，伍迪。","id":391,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/61/Avg_avg_4104_coldst_1-2$2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海伦娜","text":"那个给我留下餐厅，留下存折的家伙——知道我是什么时候遇到他的吗？","id":392,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/61/Avg_avg_4104_coldst_1-2$2.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1034_1#1$1","id":393},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伍德洛","text":"我洗耳恭听。","id":394,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/61/Avg_avg_npc_1034_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4104_coldst_1#4$2","id":395},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海伦娜","text":"十八岁。","id":396,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/39/Avg_avg_4104_coldst_1-4$2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海伦娜","text":"当时我父亲正极力把我推销给他顶头上司的儿子，好让他的职位更上一层楼。","id":397,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/39/Avg_avg_4104_coldst_1-4$2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海伦娜","text":"我得知消息后跑去酒吧待了一整晚，在那里认识了他......最后，我们骑着他的驮兽狂奔一夜，离开了那个让我窒息的地方。","id":398,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/39/Avg_avg_4104_coldst_1-4$2.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1035_1#10$1","id":399},{"type":"dialogue","name":"里昂","text":"等等，你十八岁和他私奔，可你来这里的时候已经......","id":400,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/04/Avg_avg_npc_1035_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4104_coldst_1#2$2","id":401},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海伦娜","text":"我们分开了，有二十多年没见。","id":402,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/61/Avg_avg_4104_coldst_1-2$2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海伦娜","text":"这二十多年里，我一直独自生活在拓荒地。","id":403,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/61/Avg_avg_4104_coldst_1-2$2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海伦娜","text":"你们以为，这些年过去，我连怎么在荒地上攥紧自己口袋里的金券都没学会吗？","id":404,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/61/Avg_avg_4104_coldst_1-2$2.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":405},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","posfrom":"0,0","posto":"0,-30","duration":"0.5","id":406},{"type":"charslot","duration":"0.5","id":407},{"type":"text","text":"海伦娜露出一个甜美的笑容，卸下肩上的武器，放在西尔维娅面前的桌上。","id":408},{"type":"dialog","id":409},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4104_coldst_1#1$1","duration":"0.5","posfrom":"0,-30","posto":"0,0","id":410},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":411},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海伦娜","text":"如果你们不愿加入，我会自己去做这件事。","id":412,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5c/Avg_avg_4104_coldst_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1035_1#7$1","id":413},{"type":"dialogue","name":"里昂","text":"就凭你和西尔维娅......抢银行？","id":414,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b6/Avg_avg_npc_1035_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4104_coldst_1#6$1","id":415},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海伦娜","text":"我可能会在保险库外面被抓住，可能被困死在钱堆里，也可能会死在逃跑的路上......反正，只要我还在喘气，我就要把这件事办成。","id":416,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/26/Avg_avg_4104_coldst_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海伦娜","text":"这就是我的态度。","id":417,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/26/Avg_avg_4104_coldst_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海伦娜","text":"现在，我需要你们两个人表态了。","id":418,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/26/Avg_avg_4104_coldst_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1035_1#7$1","id":419},{"type":"text","text":"里昂从腰间抽出一把扳手，放在海伦娜的武器旁边。","id":420},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4104_coldst_1#6$1","id":421},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海伦娜","text":"该你了，伍德洛——","id":422,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/26/Avg_avg_4104_coldst_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":423},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"n","id":424},{"type":"playsound","key":"$dooropenquite","id":425},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":426},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1034_1#3$1","id":427},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伍德洛","text":"谁？！","id":428,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f1/Avg_avg_npc_1034_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":429},{"type":"charslot","id":430},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1034_jesca2_1#1$1","duration":"1","id":431},{"type":"delay","time":"1.6","id":432},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4104_coldst_1#8$1","id":433},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海伦娜","text":"杰西卡？这个时候......你来做什么？","id":434,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/27/Avg_avg_4104_coldst_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1034_jesca2_1#1$1","id":435},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰西卡","text":"我......不知道。","id":436,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/44/Avg_avg_1034_jesca2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1035_1#10$1","id":437},{"type":"dialogue","name":"里昂","text":"不知道？","id":438,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/04/Avg_avg_npc_1035_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1034_jesca2_1#10$1","id":439},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰西卡","text":"但我必须去做......必须做到些什么。","id":440,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e3/Avg_avg_1034_jesca2_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1034_1#5$1","id":441},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伍德洛","text":"如果你还在想今早迈尔斯对你说的话，我的建议是别放在心上。","id":442,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_1034_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伍德洛","text":"你还有大把的时间和精力去做到很多事情，没必要把自己绑死在达维镇，或者几个日薄西山的老家伙身上。","id":443,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_1034_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1034_jesca2_1#9$1","id":444},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰西卡","text":"不，伍德洛先生......","id":445,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/26/Avg_avg_1034_jesca2_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰西卡","text":"已经太多次了，我满怀热情，最终却因为各种各样的原因......能力不足，时间不够，情况有变，或者“命令”和“要求”......","id":446,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/26/Avg_avg_1034_jesca2_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1034_jesca2_1#10$1","id":447},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰西卡","text":"就连现在，我都不知道自己能做到什么......","id":448,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e3/Avg_avg_1034_jesca2_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1034_jesca2_1#9$1","id":449},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰西卡","text":"我只能眼睁睁地看着你们被赶走，赶去前途未卜的拓荒地......","id":450,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/26/Avg_avg_1034_jesca2_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰西卡","text":"再不做到什么事情，我大概......真的会适应这样一事无成的日子。","id":451,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/26/Avg_avg_1034_jesca2_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1034_jesca2_1#7$1","id":452},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰西卡","text":"我甚至能猜到那时候的自己，为了自己心里的平衡，相信自己能力不足，相信自己本来就保护不了任何人......","id":453,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7f/Avg_avg_1034_jesca2_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰西卡","text":"相信自己举着铳从一开始就没什么特别的意义，不过就是一条选错了，却又走得太远，已经无法回头的路罢了......","id":454,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7f/Avg_avg_1034_jesca2_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1034_jesca2_1#8$1","id":455},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰西卡","text":"我不想那样......","id":456,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e4/Avg_avg_1034_jesca2_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰西卡","text":"就算是死，我都不想那样。","id":457,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e4/Avg_avg_1034_jesca2_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":458},{"type":"charslot","id":459},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西尔维娅","text":"那么......","id":460},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1034_jesca2_1#7$1","id":461},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰西卡","text":"西尔维娅小姐？","id":462,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7f/Avg_avg_1034_jesca2_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":463},{"type":"charslot","id":464},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1039_1#4$1","duration":"0.5","id":465},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":466},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西尔维娅","text":"如果现在就是你最后的一次机会......我们向银行讨回自己东西的最后机会......杰西卡，你还会帮我们吗？","id":467,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4b/Avg_avg_npc_1039_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"n","id":468},{"type":"text","text":"西尔维娅一站起来，杰西卡才看到她的脸。","id":469},{"type":"text","text":"她整张脸白得吓人，脸颊处却不自然地泛着红色，更衬得其他部分的惨白触目惊心。","id":470},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"30","ystrength":"30","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":471},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1034_1#6$1","id":472},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伍德洛","text":"够了。","id":473,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/31/Avg_avg_npc_1034_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":474},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_gunload","id":475},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":476},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1034_jesca2_1#3$1","id":477},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰西卡","text":"伍德洛先生？为什么用铳对着我？！","id":478,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/72/Avg_avg_1034_jesca2_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1034_1#6$1","id":479},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伍德洛","text":"忘掉你看到和听到的一切，离开这里吧，杰西卡。","id":480,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/31/Avg_avg_npc_1034_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1034_jesca2_1#10$1","id":481},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰西卡","text":"这到底是怎么回事？","id":482,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e3/Avg_avg_1034_jesca2_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1039_1#4$1","id":483},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西尔维娅","text":"我们要去银行......","id":484,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4b/Avg_avg_npc_1039_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1034_1#6$1","id":485},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伍德洛","text":"西尔维娅——","id":486,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/31/Avg_avg_npc_1034_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1039_1#4$1","id":487},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西尔维娅","text":"......把原本属于达维镇的东西夺回来。","id":488,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4b/Avg_avg_npc_1039_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1034_jesca2_1#3$1","id":489},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰西卡","text":"......夺回来？","id":490,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/72/Avg_avg_1034_jesca2_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1034_1#5$1","id":491},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伍德洛","text":"杰西卡，回去吧，回到你的朋友身边。","id":492,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_1034_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1034_jesca2_1#12$1","id":493},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰西卡","text":"伍德洛先生！","id":494,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c7/Avg_avg_1034_jesca2_1-12$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1034_1#5$1","id":495},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伍德洛","text":"你只是来找我们哭诉了一场，我们给你端上了一杯热水，拍了拍你的肩膀，就是这样。","id":496,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_1034_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伍德洛","text":"你还年轻，你的每一天都还是新的，真的。","id":497,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_1034_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1034_jesca2_1#14$1","id":498},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰西卡","text":"......","id":499,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_1034_jesca2_1-14$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","duration":"0.5","id":500},{"type":"text","text":"仿佛泪水被冻结干燥了似的，杰西卡的视界一下子清晰起来。","id":501},{"type":"text","text":"她看到西尔维娅脸上异常的红晕，看到桌上的扳手和陌生的武器，看到伍德洛黑洞洞的铳口。","id":502},{"type":"text","text":"她平生第一次在一个瞬间内做出决定。","id":503},{"type":"text","text":"她迎着伍德洛的铳口走了过去，走到西尔维娅身边，把腰间的铳抽出来，放在她的面前。","id":504},{"type":"dialog","id":505},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_fastener","volume":"1","id":506},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":507},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1034_jesca2_1#11$1","id":508},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰西卡","text":"算我一个。","id":509,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/03/Avg_avg_1034_jesca2_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":510},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":511},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":512},{"type":"image","id":513},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":514},{"type":"charslot","id":515},{"type":"image","id":516}],"characters":["罗拉","迈尔斯","杰西卡","车队首领","里昂","海伦娜","伍德洛","西尔维娅"]}